    loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>很久以前設定的，剛好今天 study group 分享了使用 terminal 環境的一些經驗，同事注意到我的畫面有這個，早已忘記之前怎麼設定的 XDDD</p>\n<p>在那邊試了很多關鍵字最後才找到…</p>\n<p>prompt 沒找到… production environment notifiction 也沒找到… greeting 找到了 fish 的 <code class=\"language-text\">fish_greeting</code>，welcome message 終於找到了！\n搭配 <a href=\"https://patorjk.com/software/taag/#p=display&#x26;h=0&#x26;v=0&#x26;f=ANSI%20Shadow&#x26;t=p3t.lu\">Text to ASCII Art Generator (TAAG)</a> 就可以很酷的歡迎訊息了！</p>\n<p>zsh 和 bash 的使用者可參考 <a href=\"https://tyler-j-funk.medium.com/how-i-added-an-ascii-banner-to-my-terminal-34b0a34b898e\">How I Added An ASCII Banner to My Terminal</a>。(習得關鍵字 banner)</p>\n<p>防忘，以上。</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Shell 的歡迎訊息(welcome message)","date":"August 08, 2021","description":null}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/fish-shell-load-dot-env-file/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"fish shell 讀 .env 檔設成環境變數"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/yubikey-5c-nfc/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"YubiKey 5C NFC"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"6a86e991-7f2c-5fbc-9dda-110243b66d2b","previousPostId":"7342316d-8bb1-5c2a-abf4-c60dbe504970","nextPostId":"ffcd9142-7f1e-545e-b04c-9ae60e608576"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3624854548","548598555"]}